description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '[Level 1] 10 Minute Bodyweight Workout for Starters' from the channel Jordan Yeoh Fitness.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: A 10 minutes light workout session for beginners, and anyone who just wants to do some light & easy workout. If you are a strong beginner or intermediate level trainer, you can use this video as your warm-up. Get my App here: https://bit.ly/trainwithjordanapp

Enjoy!

Estimated calories burned in this session: 50-100+ kcal
(your fitness tracker might show different results)
